OL,5,G1620 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe third visit is to The Buxted
OL,7,     FInn in Uckfield, East Sussex, run
OL,8,     Fby Nick and chef David. Lisa is
OL,9,     Fcharmed by the character, but
OL,10,     FFarid and John think it has a
OL,11,     Fcorporate feel.
OL,12,G1650 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FThe final visit is to the Crescent
OL,14,     FVictoria hotel in Margate, Kent,
OL,15,     Fwhere Farid and John hope to
OL,16,     Fdazzle their guests with a stay
OL,17,     Ffit for a queen. Can they get the
OL,18,     Fbreakfast right?
